    • Method Detail

      • drawClass

        public void drawClass(java.awt.Graphics2D g)
        Draw class on drawing panel. Set font to Arial, bold and text size. If no in or out join is found set stroke to dashed. Draw filled class rect. Draw line above methods and below variables. Draw variables and methods. Resize the size of class based on size of variables and methods.
        Parameters:
        g - Graphics2D which will handle the drawing.
